Repeat: sl 1 wyib, k4, sl 1 wyib, p2
sl 1 wyif, p4, sl 1 wyif, k2
sl 1 wyib, k4, sl 1 wyib, p2
sl 1 wyif, p4, sl 1 wyif, k2

drop slipped stitch off needle to front of work, k2, then pick up slipped stitch and knit it; slip next 2 stitches, drop slipped stitch to front of work, slip the same 2 stitches back onto left-hand needle; pick up dropped slip stitch and knit it; k2, p2
